<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HoldOff Partnerships — Let's Work Together</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Explore partnership opportunities with HoldOff. We collaborate with therapists, coaches, creators, and organizations aligned with our mission.">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1a1f3a 50%, #2d1b4e 100%);
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #c4b5fd; }

    nav a {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1.5rem;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: #a78bfa; }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #93c5fd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    .opportunities {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .opportunities { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    }

    .opp-card {
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .opp-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    }

    .opp-card h3 {
      color: #a78bfa;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .opp-card p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .form-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #a78bfa;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea,
    .form-group select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      resize: vertical;
      min-height: 100px;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus,
    .form-group select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #8b5cf6;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      margin-top: 4rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #a78bfa;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HoldOff</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live">Home</a>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Work With Us</h1>
    <p>We're looking for partners who share our mission: helping people respect themselves. Whether you're a therapist, coach, creator, or organization, let's explore how we can collaborate.</p>
    <button class="cta-btn" onclick="document.querySelector('.form-container').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">Apply Today</button>
  </section>

  <section class="opportunities">
    <div class="opp-card">
      <h3>🩺 Therapists & Counselors</h3>
      <p>Refer HoldOff to your clients as a complementary tool between sessions. We offer partner discounts and co-marketing opportunities to therapists and mental health professionals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="opp-card">
      <h3>💬 Life Coaches & Mentors</h3>
      <p>Integrate HoldOff into your coaching practice. White-label options available for coaches who want to offer their own branded version.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="opp-card">
      <h3>🎓 Organizations & Nonprofits</h3>
      <p>Bulk licenses, custom pricing, and integration partnerships for schools, universities, employee wellness programs, and nonprofits focused on mental health.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="opp-card">
      <h3>📱 App & SaaS Platforms</h3>
      <p>API partnerships and embedding opportunities for apps in the wellness, dating, relationships, and mental health spaces.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="form-container">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #a78bfa;">Apply for a Partnership</h2>
    <form method="POST" action="/api/partnership-apply" id="partnershipForm">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Jane Smith">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@example.com">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) 123-4567">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="organization">Organization / Business Name *</label>
        <input type="text" id="organization" name="organization" required placeholder="Your Company">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="type">Type of Partnership *</label>
        <select id="type" name="type" required>
          <option value="">-- Select --</option>
          <option value="therapist">Therapist / Counselor</option>
          <option value="coach">Life Coach / Mentor</option>
          <option value="nonprofit">Organization / Nonprofit</option>
          <option value="platform">App / SaaS Platform</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="details">Tell us about your partnership idea *</label>
        <textarea id="details" name="details" required placeholder="What kind of partnership are you interested in? How many users might benefit? What's your vision?"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="website">Website or Portfolio</label>
        <input type="url" id="website" name="website" placeholder="https://yourwebsite.com">
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Application</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 HoldOff. Made for people who deserve better.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/contact">Contact</a>
    </p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('partnershipForm').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const formData = new FormData(this);
      try {
        const response = await fetch('/api/partnership-apply', {
          method: 'POST',
          body: formData
        });
        if (response.ok) {
          alert('Thanks for applying! Our partnerships team will review your application and contact you within 48 hours.');
          this.reset();
        } else {
          alert('Something went wrong. Please try again.');
        }
      } catch (err) {
        console.error(err);
        alert('Error submitting application.');
      }
    });
  </script>
  <script src="/js/floating-companions.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
